{"tid":1036555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南美幫連環盜竊30萬被捕","createTime":"2019-02-25T10:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T10:55:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2bfecc4f81c84405c5d62f26f01c74ccb1adbe","tid":1036555,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190225/20620098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F20620098&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8T%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=17e6165d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190225%2F20620098&h=78e2d77d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190225/20620098</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南美幫連環盜竊30萬被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190225/large/0224szetoimg_0055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190225%2Flarge%2F0224szetoimg_0055.jpg&h=d4e9048e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名智利籍女子被捕。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】南美幫肆虐中區，於中上環及金鐘一帶食肆趁當事人不察偷走財物，短短個多月犯下五宗案件，涉及30萬元，有失主被偷去20萬元現金。警方前日於旺角拘捕三名智利籍男女，起回部份贓物。<br />\n<br />\n中區警區刑事總部重案組第二隊主管郭彥琪指，上月中起，接獲至少五宗有關南美幫的盜竊及扒竊案，賊人活躍於中上環及金鐘一帶，於區內食肆犯案。郭彥琪透露，賊人藉當事人注意力分散，將其財物盜去，甚至以利器將事主隨身袋𠝹開，再偷取財物，包括現金、手機、手提電腦等共涉及30萬元，其中一名事主被偷去約20萬元現金。<br />\n<br />\n警方經深入調查後，鎖定目標人物藏身於旺角一間賓館內，並於前日傍晚拘捕一男兩女持智利護照疑犯，年齡由35至67歲，並起回部分贓物。警方指不排除將有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n科大台學生會遭換五星旗<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n台拒引渡 泛民斥修例違初心  商界憂內地羅織罪名 敢怒不敢言"},{"pid":"2db6d3707bcbc1885425e14e4401aeece65d1c4a","tid":1036555,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"捉呢d就咁快<br />\n捉大陸蝗就放生"},{"pid":"4fa39d70e1965461c3cc1807324ba6260651c2ff","tid":1036555,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db6d3707bcbc1885425e14e4401aeece65d1c4a","tid":1036555,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"捉呢d就咁快<br />\n捉大陸蝗就放生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"一直都係"},{"pid":"91b6f7ed999810cb689d5af766051366ca91f173","tid":1036555,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db6d3707bcbc1885425e14e4401aeece65d1c4a","tid":1036555,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"捉呢d就咁快<br />\n捉大陸蝗就放生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2b4abb745808f71f38fe11d4edf53dcf57148e","tid":1036555,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"中共高壓統治下 乜撚妖魔鬼怪都出哂黎啦"}]}